# Vokop Project

**Vokop** is a CapCut-style video editing studio: upload video, edit on a timeline/canvas, translate/voiceover with AI, generate AI content (ASR/subtitles/clip assist), apply filters/transitions, and export.

## Monorepo (pnpm workspaces)

| Path | Role |
|------|------|
| `apps/web` | React 19 + Vite studio UI (port 3000) — own CapCut-style UX |
| `apps/admin` | Admin console (port 3001) |
| `services/gateway` | API entry, proxies `/api/v1/*` (port 4000) |
| `services/video-tools` | FFmpeg, sessions, jobs, editor presets (port 4001) |
| `services/auth` | Account & security only (port 4002) |
| `services/studio` | Studio projects CRUD + trash (port 4003) |
| `services/admin` | Admin RBAC, menus, users (port 4004) |
| `services/ai-content` | Studio AI: text, image, voice, translate, transcripts, agent (port 4005) |
| `packages/shared` | Config, constants, types, preferences provider |
| `packages/api` | Zod schemas, routes, typed `ApiClient` |
| `packages/ui` | Shared React components (`Button`, `LaunchButton`, …) |
| `packages/i18n` | Shared locale config; per-app JSON locales |
| `packages/db` | MongoDB + Redis helpers |

## Reference projects (architecture only)

| Source | Use in Vokop |
|--------|----------------|
| [Omniclip](https://github.com/omni-media/omniclip) | Editor **frontend core** patterns (timeline/clips, trim/split, undo/redo). Keep **own UI/UX**. |
| [FunClip](https://github.com/modelscope/FunClip) | **AI content** service design (`services/ai-content`). No Gradio UI. |
| [302.AI](https://302.ai/) | Optional **unified LLM gateway** (`provider: 302ai`) — one key for many models. |

## Commands

```bash
pnpm db:up && pnpm dev    # Mongo/Redis + all services (incl. ai-content)
pnpm dev:ai               # ai-content only
pnpm stop                 # free ports 3000–3001, 4000–4005
pnpm build                # build all packages
node --env-file=.env scripts/test-ai-302.mjs   # smoke-test 302.AI + /ai/*
```

## Conventions

- **Shared contracts** live in `@vokop/api` (schemas) and `@vokop/shared` (domain types/constants).
- **UI components** prefer `@vokop/ui` for reusable primitives. Use `@vokop/ui/antd` for Ant Design and `@vokop/ui/shadcn` for shadcn/Radix primitives — do not depend on `antd` directly in apps. Keep app-specific customization in the owning app component and promote stable shared pieces to `packages/ui`.
- **New API routes**: add Zod schema → `packages/api` client → proxy in `services/gateway` → handler in service.
- **Video session**: upload once via `POST /api/v1/video/session`; reuse `sessionId` for filmstrip, editor apply, preview, and AI jobs.
- **Studio AI**: implement in `services/ai-content` via `/api/v1/ai/*` (LLM registry: `302ai` | `gemini` | `openai` | `claude`). Prefer server APIs over client-only Gemini.
- Keep diffs minimal; match existing naming and import style (`@/` in web app).
